   - Users must comply with Google's AI usage policies
   - AI-generated insights should be treated as supportive suggestions, not prescriptions

2. User Data & Privacy:
   - Users retain ownership of their journals and personal data
   - Platform operators must comply with applicable privacy laws (GDPR/CCPA)
   - Mental health data is sensitive and must be handled with highest security standards

3. Medical Disclaimer:
